title: The Beech Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, British, Catering, English, Fusion
description: Part of the Sustainability Centre, a 55 acre site which holds courses and events related to sustainable living and renewable energy, as well as offering overnight tipi accommodation and natural burials. Sample menu items such as ploughmans, chickpea and spinach curry, banana-walnut loaf, carrot cake, and flapjacks along with coffee and tea.
streetAddress: The Sustainability Centre, Droxford Rd, East Meon
